      <heading>Fri May  7 (Shai'tan)   :: \c23Darkdream\c00</heading>
      <slot>11</slot>
      <level>203</level>
      <author>0</author>
      <date>0</date>
      <text>Darkdream is an ability ALL darkfrinds have. It is not a skill
as such but something that anyone guilded in the Darkfriend
guild can do as soon as they are guilded. It seems most of you
do not know this so here is a brief explanation of what it does

Darkdream allows any darkfriend, while sleeping to enter the 
World of Dreams. Unlike dreaming you do not dream yourself into
the room you went to sleep in but rather, you ALWAYS dream 
yourself into &quot;The Meeting Chamber&quot; Here you can give or take 
orders from other darkfriends without having to ICly leave your
place of residence (such as a novice from the Tower) to meet
with people. It can be done covertly and at any time. I have
recently redone the room and extra descriptions for the chamber
and it makes a nice little place to chat with your minions. I
encourage you to use it as an IC alternative to Gating into
places that -might- expose you and your minions.

Shai'tan
</text>
