      <heading>Sun Jun 27 (Shaidar)    :: ALL FORSAKEN</heading>
      <slot>12</slot>
      <level>203</level>
      <author>0</author>
      <date>0</date>
      <text>If you are entering another guild area, or any rp area, with the
intent or rping then be IC before and on arrival.
Please inform the GL host of that area that you intend to rp, though
you are not required to reveal what. If they are not online or you
cannot see them online post a short message telling them you intend
rp in their area.
In regard to gating into a foreign area, Gate is an IC weave and will
carry all the IC consequences. Do not gate into places like Salidar
or Tar Valon unless you have FIRSTHAND knowledge of that guilds gating
entry/exit requirements, and follow them to the letter. Otherwise you
will be forced to gate to a region outside the area and walk in using
disguise or some other similar method.
Lets keep it realistic and meet all the forms :)
</text>
